{"tid":2448883,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"支持共報！！中大中文說話5**嘅神奇(怪)人","createTime":"2021-03-16T08:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T04:44:28.000Z","uid":82169,"like":30,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"71c814f3955b1ea9f589d6077581f214ae01f1c2","tid":2448883,"uid":82169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:38:57.000Z","msg":"中大中文有個好出名嘅人，cuhk secrets都見過好幾次，但竟然冇人講！冇人講我講！<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先俾圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5DJeNji.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5DJeNji.png&h=072f8f70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話佢係黃嘅，不過佢經常話要中文科取消聽說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲話<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">共黨報講得好</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌最好以後冇人識講廣東話啦係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qp8qTZK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQp8qTZK.png&h=262e1401&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3z77nS6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3z77nS6.png&h=d98c5595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RphORMs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRphORMs.png&h=8fbf1cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日古人上身Po古文(個人自由唔屌啦)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過佢個人操守都有唔少花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F29hK7p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF29hK7p.png&h=15b0e3d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢當初中學好似中五退學，然後係咁去中大同港大旁聽，坐最前排識唔少教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二年好似比入學成績某科低過3322標準，差少少定點，反正最後都入咗中文系，令唔少人質疑佢係靠關係入大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後附上佢2019年圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZPa1sm0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZPa1sm0.png&h=bb19251f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾咁勵志<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e31f0b2ed7b00565b14a13850b3f4c5dd0718f","tid":2448883,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"そのデパートは荒っぽい人が多いだ、気をつけて。"},{"pid":"96b8fc41aab9d7ccdfb160dc3b211ae4193d0e40","tid":2448883,"uid":82169,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"56e31f0b2ed7b00565b14a13850b3f4c5dd0718f","tid":2448883,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"そのデパートは荒っぽい人が多いだ、気をつけて。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f7c871c6af5e34d0e3db3d8b335cfcb3dca791","tid":2448883,"uid":82169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:33:17.000Z","msg":"漏左多圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4b5b5ca63a6bd52e835ec6d3ce58ff98dcd61e","tid":2448883,"uid":82169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T13:50:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed059ced9730dec427a6239467abaf69c607d587","tid":2448883,"uid":82169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:48:27.000Z","msg":"訓前輕輕一推"},{"pid":"f50b6db6ef8845131bd6fd6d05186e02c075e487","tid":2448883,"uid":233866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16